---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import emailInbox from '../assets/images/email-inbox.png';
---
<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .origin-badge-wrap { margin-bottom: 32px !important; }
    .origin-timeline p { text-align: left !important; }
    .origin-conclusion p { text-align: left !important; }
  }
</style>
<section id="section-pourquoi" class="section-light section-pad" style="overflow: hidden; background:#FFFFFF; border-top:1px solid rgba(29,95,191,0.12);">
  <div class="section-inner">

    <!-- Badge — centered, accent -->
    <div class="gs-hidden origin-badge-wrap" data-gs="s2" data-gs-delay="0" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px;">
      <span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; background: var(--accent-dim); border: 1px solid var(--accent-border); border-radius: 100px; padding: 8px 20px;">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" style="flex-shrink:0;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4"/><path d="M12 8h.01"/></svg>
        <span style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--accent);">Pourquoi ce projet existe</span>
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- 2 colonnes : photo / timeline texte -->
    <div class="origin-grid">

      <!-- Colonne gauche — Photo -->
      <div class="origin-photo-col gs-hidden" data-gs="s2" data-gs-delay="0.1">
        <div class="origin-photo-wrap">
          <Image src={emailInbox} alt="34 e-mails non lus" width={760} height={424} loading="lazy" decoding="async" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:contain;" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Colonne droite — Timeline narrative -->
      <div>
        <div class="origin-timeline">

          <div class="origin-timeline-item gs-hidden" data-gs="s2" data-gs-delay="0.15">
            <div class="origin-timeline-dot"></div>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(16px,1.8vw,18px);line-height:1.75;color:var(--text-light-primary);">
              Les r&egrave;gles du commerce ont chang&eacute;.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="origin-timeline-item gs-hidden" data-gs="s2" data-gs-delay="0.25">
            <div class="origin-timeline-dot"></div>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(16px,1.8vw,18px);line-height:1.75;color:var(--text-light-primary);">
              Avant, les devis &eacute;taient remis en main propre.<br>Aujourd'hui, ils sont envoy&eacute;s par e-mail.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="origin-timeline-item gs-hidden" data-gs="s2" data-gs-delay="0.35">
            <div class="origin-timeline-dot"></div>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(16px,1.8vw,18px);line-height:1.75;color:var(--text-light-primary);">
              Avant, les particuliers s'engageaient avec l'entreprise locale.<br>Aujourd'hui, les particuliers demandent 4 ou 5 devis.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="origin-timeline-item gs-hidden" data-gs="s2" data-gs-delay="0.45">
            <div class="origin-timeline-dot"></div>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(16px,1.8vw,18px);line-height:1.75;color:var(--text-light-primary);">
              La d&eacute;cision prend donc plus de temps.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="origin-timeline-item gs-hidden" data-gs="s2" data-gs-delay="0.55">
            <div class="origin-timeline-dot"></div>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(16px,1.8vw,18px);line-height:1.75;color:var(--text-light-primary);">
              Et pendant cette p&eacute;riode, si vous ne restez pas pr&eacute;sent, votre proposition est oubli&eacute;e.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="origin-timeline-item gs-hidden" data-gs="s2" data-gs-delay="0.65">
            <div class="origin-timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="origin-conclusion">
              <p>C'est pour &eacute;viter de passer &agrave; c&ocirc;t&eacute; d'opportunit&eacute;s par manque de relance que nous d&eacute;veloppons cette solution.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
